706689f-a.title: Brooklyn: Sea Breeze Avenue - 2nd Street (West)
706689f-a.text:
318 Sea Breese Ave., at the N.W. corner of West 2nd Street, showing
the former Reception Hospital. In March 1926, it was moved to 3068 West
2nd Street.
January 1924.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
